      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom-quality condition and has been meticulously preserved by its previous owner. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior remains in pristine condition, showing no signs of wear or use. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been stored in a climate-controlled environment and maintained to the highest standards. Buyers can expect a car that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory floor.",
