    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a major project or a source of spare parts. The engine currently struggles to stay running and requires significant mechanical attention, while the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. Externally, the body shows considerable wear, including several dents, rusted panels, and fading paint, and the interior requires a complete overhaul due to extensive stains and tears. It is recommended that any potential buyer brings a trailer, as the car is not currently reliable for long-distance driving.",
